'''庫欣氏症候群'''（{{lang-fr|Le syndrome de Cushing}}；{{lang-en|Cushing's syndrome}}）亦稱'''庫欣氏症候群'''、'''柯興氏綜合徵'''、'''皮質醇增多症'''，其中包括庫欣氏病（Cushing's disease，專指由原發性腦下腺瘤所引起的庫欣氏症候群），是一種[[內分泌|內分泌]]病，是由於長時間接觸[[皮質醇|皮質醇]]或其分泌量過高而造成的一系列臨床表現與體徵<ref name=NIH2008>{{cite web|title=Cushing's Syndrome|url=http://endocrine.niddk.nih.gov/pubs/cushings/cushings.aspx#1|publisher=National Endocrine and Metabolic Diseases Information Service (NEMDIS)|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=July 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210104139/http://endocrine.niddk.nih.gov/pubs/cushings/cushings.aspx#1|archive-date=2015-02-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Forbis|first1=Pat|title=Stedman's medical eponyms|date=2005|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Baltimore, Md.|isbn=9780781754439|page=167|edition=2nd|url=https://books.google.com.ph/books?id=isqcnR6ryz0C&pg=PA167|access-date=2019-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181124003731/https://books.google.com.ph/books?id=isqcnR6ryz0C&pg=PA167|archive-date=2018-11-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其臨床表現與體徵可能包括：[[高血壓|高血壓]]、向心型肥胖（[[肚腩贅肉|肚腩有贅肉]]但雙臂與雙腿較細）、[[皮肤扩张纹|皮肤扩张纹]]（紅色或紫色的短紋）、{{le|滿月臉|Moon_facies}}（臉又圓又紅）、{{le|脂失養|Lipodystrophy}}（水牛肩，兩肩中間有一較大腫塊）、{{le|肌肉無力|Muscle weakness}}、[[骨質疏鬆|骨質疏鬆]]、[[粉刺|粉刺]]、皮膚脆弱難以癒合等<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Sym/> -->。女性患者還可能有毛髮偏多和[[月經不調|月經不調]]的症狀<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Sym/> -->。有時患者會出現情緒改變、[[頭痛|頭痛]]以及{{le|Fatigue|疲倦|長期疲倦}}等症狀<ref name=NIH2012Sym>{{cite web|title=What are the symptoms of Cushing’s syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/symptoms.aspx|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402183051/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/symptoms.aspx|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。库欣氏症状通常以皮质醇增高为代表，其行为表达会处于易激惹状态，通常很容易处于情绪化证候中而不自知。其紫纹多见于大腿根部内侧和小腹下侧，在较强的压力应激状态下易发。高皮质醇也可在单纯情绪应激时爆发，也可在长期情绪化进程中得以强化。

庫欣氏症候群的成因有可能是[[強的松|強的松]]之類的類皮質醇藥物過量，也有可能是因為[[腫瘤|腫瘤]]分泌過多皮質醇，或是腫瘤造成腎上腺製造分泌過多的皮質醇產物，進而導致出現庫興氏症候群<ref name=NIH2012Cause>{{cite web|title=What causes Cushing’s syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/causes.aspx|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402193822/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/causes.aspx|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由{{le|垂體腺瘤|pituitary adenoma}}引起的病例被稱為{{le|庫欣氏症|Cushing's disease}}<!-- <ref name=NIH2008/> -->。庫欣氏症是在藥物治療庫欣氏症候群後第二常見病症<ref name=NIH2008/>。部分的腫瘤也可能造成{{le|庫欣氏症|Cushing's disease}}<ref name=NIH2008/><ref>{{cite journal|last=Nieman|first=LK|author2=Ilias, I|title=Evaluation and treatment of Cushing's syndrome.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-medicine_2005-12_118_12/page/1340|journal=The American Journal of Medicine|date=December 2005|volume=118|issue=12|pages=1340–6|pmid=16378774|doi=10.1016/j.amjmed.2005.01.059}}</ref>。其中一些遺傳相關的病症如{{le|多發性內分泌腫瘤症候群第一型|multiple endocrine neoplasia type 1}}和{{le|Carney綜合症|Carney complex}}<ref name=NIH2012Epi/>。庫欣氏症的診斷需要一些步驟<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Diag/> -->。第一步檢查病患服用的藥物<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Diag/> -->。第二步在服用[[地塞米松|地塞米松]]後檢測[[尿液|尿液]]、[[唾液|唾液]]或[[血液|血液]]中皮質醇的濃度<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Diag/> -->。假使檢測結果為異常，可能是在深夜檢測皮質醇濃度<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Diag/> -->。假如皮質醇濃度依然很高，檢測血液中促腎上腺皮質激素可以判定是否有腦垂體異常<ref name=NIH2012Diag>{{cite web|title=How do health care providers diagnose Cushing’s syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/diagnosed.aspx|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402162423/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/diagnosed.aspx|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

大部分的病例是可以接受治療且被治癒的<ref name=NIH2012Tx>{{cite web|title=Is there a cure for Cushing’s syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/cure.aspx|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150327103924/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/cure.aspx|archive-date=2015-03-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。藉由藥物治療，這些病症通常可以慢慢減緩改善<ref name=NIH2012Tx2>{{cite web|title=What are the treatments for Cushing’s syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/treatments.aspx|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402102535/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/treatments.aspx|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。若是因為腫瘤造成庫欣氏症，則可透過外科手術配上[[化學治療|化學治療]]或[[放射治療|放射治療]]來治療<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Tx2/> -->。如果病因是腦垂體異常，可能需要額外的藥物治療來取代腦垂體失去的功能<!-- <ref name=NIH2012Tx2/> -->。經過治療後，平均壽命通常與健康人一樣<ref name=NIH2012Tx/>。有些無法透過手術切除所有腫瘤的患者死亡風險會有所提高<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Graversen|first1=D|last2=Vestergaard|first2=P|last3=Stochholm|first3=K|last4=Gravholt|first4=CH|last5=Jørgensen|first5=JO|title=Mortality in Cushing's syndrome: a systematic review and meta-analysis.|journal=European journal of internal medicine|date=April 2012|volume=23|issue=3|pages=278–82|pmid=22385888|doi=10.1016/j.ejim.2011.10.013}}</ref>

每年大約每一百萬人之中就有2至3人患上庫欣氏症候群<ref name=NIH2012Epi/>。常見於20至50歲的人<ref name=NIH2008/>。女性患病的風險是男性的三倍之多<ref name=NIH2012Epi>{{cite web|title=How many people are affected by or at risk for Cushing’s syndrome?|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/risk.aspx|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402220131/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/pages/risk.aspx|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而普遍常見的輕度皮質醇生產過剩並無明顯的病徵<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Steffensen|first1=C|last2=Bak|first2=AM|last3=Rubeck|first3=KZ|last4=Jørgensen|first4=JO|title=Epidemiology of Cushing's syndrome.|journal=Neuroendocrinology|date=2010|volume=92 Suppl 1|pages=1–5|pmid=20829610|doi=10.1159/000314297}}</ref>。在1932年，[[哈維·庫興|哈維·庫興]]最先發現庫欣氏症候群<ref>{{cite web|title=Cushing Syndrome: Condition Information|url=http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|accessdate=16 March 2015|date=2012-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402193912/http://www.nichd.nih.gov/health/topics/cushing/conditioninfo/Pages/default.aspx|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。其他動物也有可能患有庫欣氏症候群，如貓、狗和馬<ref>{{cite book|author1=Etienne Cote|title=Clinical Veterinary Advisor: Dogs and Cats|date=2014|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=9780323240741|page=502|edition=3|url=https://books.google.com.ph/books?id=NmziBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA502|access-date=2019-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180426213855/https://books.google.com.ph/books?id=NmziBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA502|archive-date=2018-04-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=McCue|first1=PM|title=Equine Cushing's disease.|journal=The Veterinary Clinics of North America. Equine Practice|date=December 2002|volume=18|issue=3|pages=533–43, viii|pmid=12516933|doi=10.1016/s0749-0739(02)00038-x}}</ref>。

